## Development

```bash
git clone https://github.com/lorenzoamir/PyBiRewire
cd PyBiRewire
pip install -e ".[dev]"
pytest            # run test suite
ruff check .      # lint
ruff format .     # format
```

Build the Jupyter tutorial notebook:

```bash
jupyter notebook notebooks/tutorial.ipynb
```

Build docs locally:

```bash
cd docs && make html
```

